<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 06:14:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>百度与联想达成第三笔中国人工智能智能手机交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-partners-with-lenovo-third-china-ai-smartphone-deal-2024-02-09/</link><description>中国的百度与联想合作，将其生成式人工智能（AI）技术应用到联想的智能手机上，这是与手机制造商的最新合作，旨在为其人工智能模型寻求实际应用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 05:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-partners-with-lenovo-third-china-ai-smartphone-deal-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：杜克能源将把中国电池巨头宁德时代从海军陆战队基地撤出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/duke-energy-remove-chinese-battery-giant-catl-marine-corps-base-2024-02-09/</link><description>在国会的压力下，美国公用事业公司杜克能源公司计划退役中国电池制造商宁德时代在美国最大的海军陆战队基地之一生产的储能电池。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 05:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/duke-energy-remove-chinese-battery-giant-catl-marine-corps-base-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>避险需求抵消美元走强，金价持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-flat-safe-haven-demand-offsets-us-dollar-strength-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五，由于中国市场因农历新年假期休市，黄金价格在清淡交易中持平，而美元坚挺抵消了中东担忧引发的避险需求。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-flat-safe-haven-demand-offsets-us-dollar-strength-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国新年旅游高峰进入高潮，中国增加了创纪录的火车数量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-new-year-travel-rush-kicks-into-high-gear-country-adds-record-number-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五，中国在一年一度的农历新年假期前夕进入了高潮，旅客们挤上火车和飞机返回家乡，与家人一起准备传统的团圆饭聚会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-new-year-travel-rush-kicks-into-high-gear-country-adds-record-number-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>第三季度财报突显中国担忧，日产股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-shares-slump-q3-results-highlight-china-worries-competition-2024-02-09/</link><description>日产汽车 (Nissan Motor) 下调了本财年的销量预期，且对其中国业务感到担忧，周五该公司股价暴跌 11.7%，这可能是自 2001 年以来的最大跌幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 02:17:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-shares-slump-q3-results-highlight-china-worries-competition-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数创新高，中国新年假期紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-09/</link><description>日本股市周五触及 34 年来的新高，世界股市有望连续第三周上涨，而利率预期的调整则导致日元跌至两个月低点，澳元和新西兰元则走势相反。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 02:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑采取限制措施将中国“智能汽车”拒之门外 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-considering-curbs-keep-chinese-smart-cars-out-country-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</link><description>彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道称，由于美国对数据安全的担忧日益加剧，拜登政府正在考虑限制进口中国“智能汽车”及相关零部件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-considering-curbs-keep-chinese-smart-cars-out-country-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>日元触及10周低点，美元走强，交易员调整利率押注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-near-10-week-low-dollar-buoyant-traders-adjust-rate-bets-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五日元跌至10周低点，而美元则连续第四周上涨，因为交易员减少了对日本央行将多快加息以及美联储将多快降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-near-10-week-low-dollar-buoyant-traders-adjust-rate-bets-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>泰国、马来西亚、新加坡希望通过免签旅游吸引中国人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-malaysia-singapore-hope-lure-chinese-with-visa-free-travel-2024-02-09/</link><description>中国工程师兼航空爱好者魏明正是新加坡、马来西亚和泰国旅游部门正在寻找的游客。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-malaysia-singapore-hope-lure-chinese-with-visa-free-travel-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>英国基金经理阿什莫尔退出对中国恒大的押注 - 彭博新闻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/uk-fund-manager-ashmore-exited-bet-china-evergrande-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</link><description>据彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道，英国安石集团（Ashmore Group）曾是中国恒大集团海外债务的主要持有者，去年年底完全退出了对这家中国房地产开发商的投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:09:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/uk-fund-manager-ashmore-exited-bet-china-evergrande-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>尽管寻求更大的中国贸易，危地马拉仍与台湾保持关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/guatemala-maintain-taiwan-ties-despite-seeking-greater-china-trade-2024-02-08/</link><description>危地马拉总统贝尔纳多·阿雷瓦洛周四表示，尽管寻求与中国建立更紧密的经济联系，但无意与台湾断绝外交关系，并承诺同时加强与两国的关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 23:24:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/guatemala-maintain-taiwan-ties-despite-seeking-greater-china-trade-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平与普京通话时敦促“密切战略协作”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-urges-close-strategic-coordination-call-with-putin-2024-02-08/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平向俄罗斯总统普京表示，两国应密切战略协作，捍卫各自国家的主权、安全和发展利益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-urges-close-strategic-coordination-call-with-putin-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>“消防员”吴在溃败后成为中国市场监管者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/firefighter-wu-becomes-chinas-market-regulator-after-rout-2024-02-08/</link><description>中国市场监管机构的新任负责人对内幕交易采取强硬态度，迅速扑救，与共产党领导人密切合作，并管理过一家证券交易所——这对于掌管中国陷入困境的股市的人来说是完美的形象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/firefighter-wu-becomes-chinas-market-regulator-after-rout-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>一年过去了，一位中国明星交易撮合者的缺席给他的银行蒙上了一层阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/one-year-star-chinese-dealmakers-absence-casts-pall-over-his-bank-2024-02-08/</link><description>包凡被中国当局带走，此后同事就再也没有见过他。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 09:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/one-year-star-chinese-dealmakers-absence-casts-pall-over-his-bank-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>1月份中国乘用车销量环比下降14.1%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-passenger-vehicle-sales-fall-141-jan-mm-2024-02-08/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周四公布的数据显示，1月份中国乘用车销量环比下降14.1%，这是自8月份以来首次出现下滑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:14:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-passenger-vehicle-sales-fall-141-jan-mm-2024-02-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>